detailedForecast: A chance of rain showers between midnight and 2am, then rain showers likely and patchy fog. Mostly cloudy, with a low around 49. Southwest wind 7 to 10 mph, with gusts as high as 23 mph. Chance of precipitation is 60%. New rainfall amounts less than a tenth of an inch possible.
